    <h2>What not to claim from an SSD upgrade</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Do not expect a guaranteed FPS increase. Storage can affect install speed, patching, transfers, and some load behavior, but this page does not claim measured frame-rate gains.</li>
      <li>Do not assume a hotter/faster desktop drive is better in a handheld shell.</li>
      <li>Do not rely on marketplace compatibility text when the manufacturer spec page says something different.</li>
      <li>Do not buy a drive with an attached heatsink unless the handheld's service guidance explicitly supports that thickness.</li>
    </ul>

